        "id": 1019142
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-03-09T09:46:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "as much as possible, we prefer declarations at the begining of the function. I know rbh_values can be hard to work with since everything is const. There are a few helper functions in librobinhood to help manage this. I recommend that you look at other backends to see how you can do this. The posix backend might be a good example for this.",
